    47	/// A penalty matrix that may be stored in Kronecker-factored form.
    48	///
    49	/// For tensor-product terms (e.g. time-varying survival covariates), the penalty
    50	/// has the structure `S = left ⊗ right` (Kronecker product). Keeping this
    51	/// factored avoids materializing (p_left × p_right)² dense entries and enables
    52	/// exact log-determinant computation via `log|A ⊗ B| = n_B log|A| + n_A log|B|`.
    53	///
    54	/// Dense penalties are stored as-is.  Callers that need a raw `Array2<f64>` can
    55	/// call `as_dense()` (zero-cost for Dense, lazy-materialized for KroneckerFactored).
