    63	    /// Block-local penalty: `local` is `block_dim × block_dim`, embedded at
    64	    /// `col_range` in the full parameter space of dimension `total_dim`.
    65	    /// Avoids materializing the full `total_dim × total_dim` matrix.
    66	    Blockwise {
